          Show that if <m>y(0)=\sqrt{\frac{h}{w}}</m> and
          <m>\brackeval{\dfdx{y}{x}}{x}{0}=0</m>, then <m>A=B=\frac12{}\sqrt{\frac{h}{w}}</m>. Compare this to the equation of the
